df$public_ter <- cut(
  df$public,
  breaks = quantile(df$public, probs = seq(0, 1, length.out = 4), na.rm = TRUE),
  include.lowest = TRUE,
  labels = c("T1(최저)", "T2(중간)", "T3(최고)")
)

fit_pub_ter <- survfit(Surv(time, event) ~ public_ter, data = df)

ggsurvplot(
  fit_pub_ter,
  data = df,
  conf.int = TRUE,
  risk.table = TRUE,
  ggtheme = theme_bw(),
  palette = "Dark2",
  xlab = "Time",
  ylab = "Survival Probability",
  legend.title = "Public(3분위)"
)
## Ignoring unknown labels:
## • colour : "Public(3분위)"

# Schoenfeld 잔차 기반 PH 가정 검정
ph_test <- cox.zph(cox_model)
ph_test
##             chisq df       p
## busdist    5.3094  1   0.021
## subdist    0.1886  1   0.664
## com        1.7090  1   0.191
## com_small  2.8958  1   0.089
## public     0.0725  1   0.788
## mp         5.4482  1   0.020
## GLOBAL    34.5584  6 5.2e-06
plot(ph_test)

ggcoxdiagnostics(
  cox_model,
  type = "deviance",
  ggtheme = theme_bw()
)
## `geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

ggforest(cox_model, data = df)
